    "Combined with Table 3 and Figs.",
    "5 and 6, it can be illustrated that the TCN-GRU model embedded in the ECA module effectively improves the prediction performance, has higher prediction accuracy, and can achieve better power generation forecasting results.",
    "The robustness of the proposed model is also verified by prediction experiments conducted during multiple seasons.",
